3. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper deals with improving the performance of neural networks by reducing computation time and model size. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a method to improve the efficiency of AI models for image classification tasks. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with improving the performance of DCNN models for image classification tasks, which is a common application of multimedia technology.
